      • checkIn

        public static void checkIn()
        Prompts user for passport details to check in. Will update room status and reservation status accordingly.

      • checkOut

        public static void checkOut()
        Prompts user for room number to check out. Print bill invoice and ask for payment via cash or credit card For credit card will prompt user on whether to use existing credit card number or a new credit card number Update reservation and room status accordingly

      • checkRoomAvailability

        public static void checkRoomAvailability()
        Prompts for room number and shows the status of the room if it exists.

      • createGuest

        public static void createGuest()
        Prompts for passport of the guest. If the guest already exists, it will return back to calling function. Else it will prompt for more user input for the necessary attributes to create Guest object and update the guest data file.

      • createMenuItem

        public static void createMenuItem()
        Prompts for item name. If the item already exists, it will return back to calling function. Else it will prompt for more user input for the necessary attributes to create Item object and update the item data file.

      • createReservation

        public static void createReservation()
        Prompts for passport of the guest. If the guest does not exists, it will prompt to create a guest. Else it will prompt for more user input for the necessary attributes to create Reservation object and update the reservation data file.

      • createRoom

        public static void createRoom()
        Prompts for room number. If the room does not exists, it will return back to calling function. Else it will prompt for more user input for the necessary attributes to create ROom object and update the Room data file.

      • createRoomServiceOrder

        public static void createRoomServiceOrder()
        Prompts for room number of the guest. If the reservation object does not exist, it will return back to calling function. Else it will prompt for more user input for the necessary attributes to create Service object and update the service data file.

      • searchGuest

        public static void searchGuest()
        Search for a guest based on a keyword guest name. Shows a list of guests that have the same name that the user input.

      • updateGuest

        public static void updateGuest()
        Prompts for passport of the guest. If guest does not exist, it will return back to calling function. Else it will prompt the user which attributes to update.

      • updateMenuItem

      • updateReservation

        public static void updateReservation()
        Prompts for reservation code. If reservation does not exist, it will return back to calling function. Else it will prompt the user which attributes to update.

      • updateRoom

        public static void updateRoom()
        Prompts for room number. If room does not exist, it will return back to calling function. Else it will prompt the user which attributes to update.

      • updateRoomServiceOrder

        public static void updateRoomServiceOrder()
        Prompts for room number. If room does not exist, it will return back to calling function. Else it will display a list of room service orders that the room has made. Next it will prompt the user to input a serviceID to update.
